				\begin{document}$$N=150$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M16"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>N</mml:mi><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mn>150</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12968_2021_791_Article_IEq8.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> consecutively acquired cases (sample D<sub>2</sub>), the chronologically first <inline-formula id="IEq9"><alternatives><tex-math id="M17">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
