      <p id="Par30">At our institution, <italic>Atri-U</italic> is implemented in the clinical routine, as previously described [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR16">16</xref>]. For each qualifying CMR study, <italic>Atri-U</italic> is automatically triggered and it takes approximately 120 s until the automatically calculated <inline-formula id="IEq38"><alternatives><tex-math id="M75">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
